#: ../../differences/python_310.rst:6
msgid ""
"Python 3.10.0 (final) was released on the 4 October 2021. The Features "
"for 3.10 are defined in `PEP 619 "
"<https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0619/#features-for-3-10>`_ and a "
"detailed description of the changes can be found in `What's New in Python"
" 3.10 <https://docs.python.org/3/whatsnew/3.10.html>`_."
msgstr ""
"Python 3.10.0(最终版本)于2021年10月4日发布。3.10的特性在 `PEP 619 "
"<https://www.python.org/dev/peps/pep-0619/#features-for-3-10>`_ 中定义，"
"有关更改的详细描述可以在 `What's New in Python 3.10 <https://docs.python.org/"
"3/whatsnew/3.10.html>`_ 中找到。"

